OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1774293066
OL,3,CCalls for Queen's University to act
OL,4,Cafter poll calls for Irish signage
OL,6,FThere have been calls for Queen's
OL,7,FUniversity to act 'immediately' to
OL,8,Fintroduce Irish language signs after
OL,9,Fthousands voted in a students' union
OL,10,Fpoll.
OL,12,FHowever, those opposed said the move
OL,13,Fwould have a 'chilling effect' for
OL,14,Funionist students.
OL,16,FIrish language signs were removed from
OL,17,Fthe campus almost 30 years ago after
OL,18,Fcalls from some unionist students and
OL,19,Fa recommendation by the Fair
OL,20,FEmployment Commission for a more
OL,21,F'neutral working environment'.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/16
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
