FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1774293066
OL,3,CCalls for Queen's University to act
OL,4,Cafter poll calls for Irish signage
OL,6,FThe latest all-student vote was
OL,7,Forganised by Queen's Students' Union.
OL,8,FThe poll also backed Irish and English
OL,9,Fbeing given equal status by the
OL,10,Funiversity.
OL,12,FAs the university is a separate entity
OL,13,Fto the union it is not compelled to
OL,14,Ftake any action on the outcome.
OL,16,FHowever, prior to the vote it was said
OL,17,Fthe university positively engaged with
OL,18,Fthe idea to implement a change to its
OL,19,Fsigns pending the result. Queen's did
OL,20,Fnot comment on this matter.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/16
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1774293066
OL,3,CCalls for Queen's University to act
OL,4,Cafter poll calls for Irish signage
OL,6,FFollowing the result there have been
OL,7,Fcalls for the university to act
OL,8,Fimmediately, while a unionist
OL,9,Frepresentative said changes to signage
OL,10,Fto incorporate Irish would have a
OL,11,F'chilling effect'.
OL,13,FQueen's said it was waiting to see the
OL,14,Foutcome of the Irish language
OL,15,Fcommissioner's work on signage at
OL,16,Fpublic buildings and would work with
OL,17,Fthe respective language commissioners.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/16
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1774293066
OL,3,CCalls for Queen's University to act
OL,4,Cafter poll calls for Irish signage
OL,6,FOut of the 5,088 students who voted,
OL,7,F91% (4,607) were in favour of the
OL,8,Fchanges to campus signage and policy,
OL,9,Fwhile 407 voted against.
OL,11,FThe vote also asked if the
OL,12,Funiversity's name and logo should
OL,13,Fappear in both English and Irish. It
OL,14,Falso gauged support for a new policy
OL,15,Fthat would treat Irish and English as
OL,16,Fequal official languages at the
OL,17,Finstitution.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/16
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1774293066
OL,3,CCalls for Queen's University to act
OL,4,Cafter poll calls for Irish signage
OL,6,FThe turnout represented around 20% of
OL,7,FQUB's 25,000 student body. The
OL,8,FStudent's Union will now campaign to
OL,9,Freinstate the signs on campus.
OL,11,FEoghan O Conghaile from An Cumann
OL,12,FGaelach, a student society that
OL,13,Fpromotes the Irish language, called
OL,14,Ffor the 'immediate' reinstatement of
OL,15,Fdual language signage.
OL,26,@sD@Hrg
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/16
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1774293066
OL,3,CCalls for Queen's University to act
OL,4,Cafter poll calls for Irish signage
OL,6,FHe said: "Tremendous feeling to see
OL,7,Fthe vote go the way we were expecting,
OL,8,Fand from this we can then take this
OL,9,Fand go to the senior management at the
OL,10,FQueen's University of Belfast who we
OL,11,Fhave met before on a few occasions,
OL,12,Fand this then gives us An Cumann
OL,13,FGaelach a democratic mandate."
OL,15,F"This shows that it is not just
OL,16,Fincoming Gaelacht calling for this,
OL,17,Fthis is something the vast population
OL,18,Fof Queen's the student base, want to
OL,19,Fsee.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/16
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1774293066
OL,3,CCalls for Queen's University to act
OL,4,Cafter poll calls for Irish signage
OL,6,F"This is something that 20% of the
OL,7,Fstudent body has voted on and it's
OL,8,Fclear that this is an issue that
OL,9,Fpeople take a great interest in and
OL,10,Ffrom the next.
OL,12,F"Going forward I suppose would be to
OL,13,Fliaise with senior management and to
OL,14,Fand we're confident that we can get
OL,15,Fsome positive developments on an
OL,16,Fimmediate basis.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/16
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1774293066
OL,3,CCalls for Queen's University to act
OL,4,Cafter poll calls for Irish signage
OL,6,F"This can actually foster good
OL,7,Fcommunity relations and there's no
OL,8,Fwish or regard for the removal of
OL,9,FEnglish languages on campus, but it's
OL,10,Fmore the campaign towards inclusivity
OL,11,Fand equality to see both communities
OL,12,Frepresented in equal status on the
OL,13,Fphysical infrastructure of this
OL,14,Funiversity."
OL,16,FJay Basra, chairman of QUB Young
OL,17,FUnionists, said he would accept the
OL,18,Fvote but does not believe it would
OL,19,Flead to any change.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/16
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1774293066
OL,3,CCalls for Queen's University to act
OL,4,Cafter poll calls for Irish signage
OL,6,FSpeaking to UTV he said: "Our message
OL,7,Fhas been quite simple, we want an
OL,8,Finclusive student union, the student
OL,9,Funion is supposed to represent all
OL,10,Fstudents, and that's what we've been
OL,11,Fpushing for.
OL,13,F"We believe that this proposal has
OL,14,Fbeen carried for by the student union
OL,15,Fwhile not giving due course for other
OL,16,Fproposals that we've put forward in
OL,17,Fthe past and we've campaigned on.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/16
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1774293066
OL,3,CCalls for Queen's University to act
OL,4,Cafter poll calls for Irish signage
OL,6,F"And that's our sort of strong message
OL,7,Fat the centre of it all. I think if
OL,8,Fsignage is erected, it'll have a
OL,9,Fchilling effect as it did in 1997, and
OL,10,Fthat's why they were removed initially.
OL,12,F"It's quite clear that this policy
OL,13,Fwon't lead to signage, and that's
OL,14,Fsomething we must be clear about. This
OL,15,Fthe university has its own mechanisms,
OL,16,Fthe student union has its own policy
OL,17,Ffile, and that's the key difference.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/16
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44311
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1774293066
OL,3,CCalls for Queen's University to act
OL,4,Cafter poll calls for Irish signage
OL,6,F"I think as most things in Northern
OL,7,FIreland, signage has become a
OL,8,Fpolitical subject, it's been
OL,9,Fpoliticised. And look, we have to
OL,10,Fbring everyone together for making a
OL,11,Fdecision on what might be a divisive
OL,12,Fpolicy. And this using of a binary
OL,13,Fvote has not been that."
OL,15,FSorcha McGarry, a medicine student
OL,16,Fsays the Irish language is becoming
OL,17,Fmore diverse, with friends from
OL,18,Fdifferent backgrounds learning the
OL,19,Flangauge.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G11/16
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44312
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1774293066
OL,3,CCalls for Queen's University to act
OL,4,Cafter poll calls for Irish signage
OL,6,FShe said: "Irish is my first language.
OL,7,FIt would be really nice to see it here
OL,8,Frepresented at Queen's on an everyday
OL,9,Fbasis. I use Irish every day, I speak
OL,10,Fwith my friends and my family, so I
OL,11,Fwould really like to see it
OL,12,Frepresented.
OL,14,F"I've also spoken to so many people
OL,15,Fwho would be keen to learn Irish, even
OL,16,Fif they're not from the sort of
OL,17,Fstereotypical background that people
OL,18,Fthink Irish is for`because Irish is
OL,19,Freally for everyone.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G12/16
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44313
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1774293066
OL,3,CCalls for Queen's University to act
OL,4,Cafter poll calls for Irish signage
OL,6,F"Nobody is suggesting taking the
OL,7,FEnglish off the signs or trying to
OL,8,Ftake away anyone else's culture; all
OL,9,Fwe're doing is wanting to add to it,
OL,10,Fand add such a beautiful, ancient
OL,11,Flanguage to our campus."
OL,13,FIn a statement Queen's added: "The
OL,14,Foutcome of the Queen's Students' Union
OL,15,FIrish language referendum reflects
OL,16,Fstrong student engagement in an
OL,17,Fimportant campus debate.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G13/16
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44314
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1774293066
OL,3,CCalls for Queen's University to act
OL,4,Cafter poll calls for Irish signage
OL,6,F"Student perspectives are a valued
OL,7,Fpart of the university community and
OL,8,Fcontribute to ongoing discussions
OL,9,Faround inclusion, identity and
OL,10,Fcultural expression.
OL,12,F"The university already has strong
OL,13,FIrish language provision and will
OL,14,Fcontinue to support and promote it as
OL,15,Fpart of campus life.
OL,17,F"The university has proactively
OL,18,Fengaged with both the Irish Language
OL,19,FCommissioner and the Commissioner for
OL,20,FUlster Scots and the Ulster British
OL,21,FTradition.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G14/16
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44315
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1774293066
OL,3,CCalls for Queen's University to act
OL,4,Cafter poll calls for Irish signage
OL,6,F"As the Irish Language Commissioner
OL,7,Fnoted during his recent lecture as
OL,8,Fpart of our Seachtain na Gaeilge
OL,9,F(Irish language week) programme, he is
OL,10,Fcurrently developing proposals for
OL,11,Fpublic institutions and has asked for
OL,12,Fthe time and space to complete this
OL,13,Fwork.
OL,15,F"We look forward to working with both
OL,16,Fcommissioners on their proposals to
OL,17,Fthe Northern Ireland Executive, which
OL,18,Fwill help guide the university as it
OL,19,Fprogresses work relating to language,
OL,20,Fculture and identity and inform our
OL,21,Fnext steps."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G15/16
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
